prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a minimalist and humorous birthday greeting card. Clean, flat 2D vector illustration with simple shapes and a soft pastel color palette on a solid cream-colored background.

In the center, a cartoon illustration of Lao Lao from the reference photo, wearing her blue sweatshirt (no logo), is comically trying to balance a precarious, towering stack of giant boba drinks. Her expression is one of playful concentration and delight. To her right, a cartoon illustration of Jordan from the reference photo, wearing his brown hoodie, holds a giant, oversized boba straw, poised and ready to help her drink from the towering stack.

Scattered around their feet are two small, cute, cartoon dogs of different breeds, playfully jumping and trying to get a lick of the boba drinks. One dog is a fluffy white Samoyed and the other is a happy golden retriever, both with birthday party hats on. Simple, elegant boba pearl shapes float gently in the background like confetti.

Centered in the middle of the composition, in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao".
